  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-pentagon-magenta.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, you can shield yourself and others with telekinetic force. As a bonus action, you can choose creatures, which can include you, that you can see within 30 feet of you, up to a number of creatures equal to your <strong>Intelligence modifier</strong> (minimum of one creature). Each of the chosen creatures is protected by <strong>half cover</strong> for 1 minute or until you're incapacitated.</p>\n<p>Once you take this bonus action, you can't do so again until you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>, unless you expend a @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.ZiuqJbJNPDWwW8No]{Psionic Energy} die to take it again.</p>",
